869
00:36:56,580 --> 00:36:57,820
The will to draw?

870
00:36:58,580 --> 00:36:59,380
What is that?

871
00:37:00,780 --> 00:37:02,260
You need to find a reason to draw your sword.

872
00:37:04,460 --> 00:37:04,940
(That's right.)

873
00:37:05,460 --> 00:37:06,620
The sword forged by Sword Heart Tomb

874
00:37:06,740 --> 00:37:07,740
is indeed different.

875
00:37:08,060 --> 00:37:08,980
It's said that the last step

876
00:37:08,980 --> 00:37:09,900
of their sword forging

877
00:37:10,020 --> 00:37:11,900
was to make their palm bleed
and feed the sword with blood.

878
00:37:12,340 --> 00:37:13,660
So the swords that were forged in the end

879
00:37:14,180 --> 00:37:15,300
were said to have souls.

880
00:37:16,820 --> 00:37:17,780
But with your talent,

881
00:37:18,660 --> 00:37:19,860
drawing the sword is only a matter of time.

882
00:37:22,020 --> 00:37:22,940
Since it's rare for you to be here,

883
00:37:23,500 --> 00:37:25,180
why don't we go and have a drink?

884
00:37:25,660 --> 00:37:26,180
Good idea.

885
00:37:26,380 --> 00:37:27,220
I do have one more thing

886
00:37:27,420 --> 00:37:28,620
to ask you.

887
00:37:30,420 --> 00:37:31,740
He knows a lot of things.

888
00:37:32,300 --> 00:37:33,140
Why do you need

889
00:37:33,380 --> 00:37:34,140
to ask me?

890
00:37:34,740 --> 00:37:35,420
Am I right?

891
00:37:37,180 --> 00:37:39,420
I want to ask about Master Lei Hong,

892
00:37:39,740 --> 00:37:40,580
Master Li Hanyi,

893
00:37:40,980 --> 00:37:42,300
and Tao Sword Deity of Mount Wangcheng,

894
00:37:42,540 --> 00:37:43,180
Zhao Yuzhen.

895
00:37:43,660 --> 00:37:44,580
(What kind of story do they have)

896
00:37:44,980 --> 00:37:46,220
(between the three of them?)

897
00:37:55,860 --> 00:37:57,300
(Miss, who are you?)

898
00:37:58,780 --> 00:38:03,340
[Mount Wangcheng]

899
00:38:11,180 --> 00:38:14,900
[Zhao Yuzhen, Mount Wangcheng]

900
00:38:15,780 --> 00:38:19,500
