901
00:38:21,300 --> 00:38:24,380
♪Alas, one thought is all it takes to reunite♪

902
00:38:24,500 --> 00:38:26,140
♪One thought is all it takes to part♪

903
00:38:26,300 --> 00:38:28,820
♪I can't endure this life of tribulations♪

904
00:38:30,540 --> 00:38:31,860
♪The beautiful seasons♪

905
00:38:32,090 --> 00:38:40,060
♪Are just our fates intertwined♪

906
00:38:42,140 --> 00:38:46,100
♪A romance and an obsession♪

907
00:38:46,260 --> 00:38:50,580
♪Tears can't move my thoughts away
from whatever they are so focused on♪

908
00:38:50,660 --> 00:38:52,220
♪Deep love doesn't last long♪

909
00:38:52,460 --> 00:38:57,100
♪Who to say goodbye to?♪

910
00:38:59,500 --> 00:39:03,460
♪A lifetime of longing for the love
of half a lifetime♪

911
00:39:03,700 --> 00:39:07,060
♪The season will never grow old,
and this love will last forever♪

912
00:39:07,340 --> 00:39:09,540
♪When all at once I turn my head♪

913
00:39:09,780 --> 00:39:14,420
♪I find you there
where lantern light is dimly shed♪

914
00:39:14,660 --> 00:39:15,900
Miss, who are you?

915
00:39:17,140 --> 00:39:18,140
How did you know I'm a lady?

916
00:39:18,940 --> 00:39:19,700
All you did was wear a man's clothes

917
00:39:19,700 --> 00:39:21,020
and apply a fake mustache.

918
00:39:22,020 --> 00:39:22,980
Only the child
who's guarding the small mountain path

919
00:39:23,020 --> 00:39:23,900
would fall for that trick.

920
00:39:24,020 --> 00:39:25,020
So you're Zhao Yuzhen?

921
00:39:25,860 --> 00:39:27,380
Yes, I'm Zhao Yuzhen.

922
00:39:27,980 --> 00:39:28,860
Why don't you come and sit with me?

923
00:39:29,380 --> 00:39:30,340
We'll have peaches in a while.

924
00:39:31,060 --> 00:39:31,780
Peaches?

925
00:39:32,540 --> 00:39:33,020
Yes, peaches.

926
00:39:33,780 --> 00:39:34,900
I infused my wooden sword

927
00:39:35,140 --> 00:39:36,260
