931
00:39:40,700 --> 00:39:42,060
Fire Formation Secret Arts?

932
00:39:43,100 --> 00:39:44,260
It's the top-level mental cultivation method
of Mount Wangcheng.

933
00:39:45,140 --> 00:39:46,380
And you're using it to grow peaches?

934
00:39:47,460 --> 00:39:49,300
Or else what's the point of learning it?

935
00:39:53,420 --> 00:39:54,740
I'm Li Hanyi from Xueyue City.

936
00:39:55,780 --> 00:39:56,940
I heard you're the youngest celestial master

937
00:39:57,100 --> 00:39:58,940
in the history of Mount Wangcheng.

938
00:39:59,580 --> 00:40:00,740
I'm here to ask you to show your swordsmanship.

939
00:40:02,620 --> 00:40:03,700
Xueyue City?

940
00:40:04,900 --> 00:40:05,860
Li Hanyi?

941
00:40:07,620 --> 00:40:08,620
These words sound pretty cold

942
00:40:08,980 --> 00:40:09,860
