945
00:40:13,220 --> 00:40:14,900
Stop talking nonsense. Eat this!

946
00:40:25,260 --> 00:40:26,020
Taiyi Lion Secret Arts?

947
00:40:27,940 --> 00:40:28,740
I'm here to test your swordsmanship.

948
00:40:29,300 --> 00:40:30,420
So don't fight me with such a spell.

949
00:40:32,340 --> 00:40:33,180
Can't you be reasonable?

950
00:40:33,620 --> 00:40:34,500
